05:41.932 --> 05:43.932
<b></font></b> <i>The few medical and
military personnel left</i>

05:43.934 --> 05:47.068
<i>searched desperately
for Patient Zero.</i>

05:47.070 --> 05:50.505
<i>Hoping that from his blood we
can engineer an anti-virus.</i>

05:56.612 --> 05:59.981
<i>There is no reasoning
