06:03.987 --> 06:06.087
<i>Except for me.</i>

06:06.089 --> 06:07.957
<i>I can speak their language.</i>

06:08.857 --> 06:10.724
<i>Why?</i> </font></b>

06:10.726 --> 06:13.760
<i>I've been bitten,
